Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(180,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H2D2F93&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrifying Giant! King Dark Emerges!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What lovely flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, I'll get you one! Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come down too, Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a weird cave...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, watch your step...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so weird about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet and listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You think there's a monster in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It must come out somewhere else.\NWe're just hearing the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I heard there's\Ncaves connected to Mt. Fuji around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They probably spread all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Connected to Mt. Fuji...?\NWhat a find!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, it's just a statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But what's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at it gives me the creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Its eyes opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run for it, Sanae! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sucking me in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Big brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're all here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Khan Condor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Toad Goemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpion Geronimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Beetle Lupin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Khan Condor, the real Genghis\NKhan killed countless people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Combine that devilish spirit\Nwith the ferocity of the condor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Condor can do no less!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that power you possess to\Nthrow all Japan into disarray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My Vampire Plan all begins\Nwith one sacrifice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wipe the X Rider off the face of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, X Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Up with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo! Is your shift over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...Are those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't take flowers to a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not exactly Keisuke's area...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I... just don't know\Nmany young ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me? And what are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding, how rude can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry... Ok, off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, this guy just can't take a hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lay off those two a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in real trouble if they quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're having a tough time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are they going to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems her big brother went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1\i1}Yamagami Hospital\NInternal medicine, surgery, pediatrics\NDirector: Yamagami Hajime{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gorgeous... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking better than we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be over this in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! My brother died protecting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I didn't mean to upset you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should leave. We don't\Nwant her to fall back into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alright.\N-Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-See you!\N-Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae, my loyal blood slave...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, master...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about your two friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mako and Chiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...work at Tachibana's coffee shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana's coffee shop? So,\Nthey're the X Rider's two allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae's not doing so well, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... She did just\Nlose her brother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I get the feeling\Nthat's not the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nsomething does feel a little off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...Is it me, or are we being watched?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this park is kinda creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chiko!!\N-What should we do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Run for it!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look like\None of GOD's monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Genghis Khan Condor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Khan Condor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life is mine, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Khan Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mini condors, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You too will become my slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider! Next time you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now. Go\Nto Tachibana's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right.\N-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still so gloomy...\NC'mon, drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is he after...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, can you get these\Ntwo to a safe place by 1pm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A safe place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A downtown hotel should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we know what Genghis\NKhan Condor wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...we've got to keep these two safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll find them a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok.\N-Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't let anyone\Nbut me or the chief in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be safe on\Nthe thirty-second floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never want to see\Nthat monster's face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you won't if you're careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bed! We never\Nget breaks like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing gets you down, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, blood slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tachibana told me. It's so\Nawful what happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I was ordered to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordered to!? By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By my master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your master!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanae!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you will join me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Genghis Khan...\N-...Condor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, become vampires!\NBecome my blood slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then infest the city and bring\Nmore humans to our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chiko!\N-Mako!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting reports that a\Nstrange virus is spreading citywide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Young women are assuming the appearance and\Nmannerisms of what can only be called vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause has yet to be identified, but the\Npolice ask that you not go out alone at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In other news--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him. It has to be\NGenghis Khan Condor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like his plan is to turn\Neveryone in Japan into vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Things will only get\Nworse if we don't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But where's he hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me! Please, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there! You're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She bit my wrist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...You were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A little longer and\Nyou'd be a vampire too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Khan Condor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you turning these\Npeople into vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those two? Disappearing\Nwhen you try to do them a favour...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something we want more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut to the chase, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys... That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even thirstier after\Nbeing interrupted once today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't tell me you're really--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he got you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle-aged blood is lousy! No flavour!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so close to catching\None of those vampires...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, how about a coffee?\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take him to the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, my slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Jin Keisuke, too, will\Nbecome a loyal vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think your vampire\Nvirus would affect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him, my slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave a drop of his blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to fight... Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish X Rider, I haven't lost yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, just try and foll--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Genghis Khan Condor!\NYou're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser Big Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going, Cruiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Genghis Khan Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! I can't breathe fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His vampire virus will\Ndisappear with his body...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the others will return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Your fangs...\N-...are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.40,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:23:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD's King Dark has appeared in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the X Rider rises to oppose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.10,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A scientist hides the blueprints\Nfor GOD's latest terrible weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark dispatches Gama Goemon,\Na monster with a great thief's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight on, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"King Dark! Demonic Invention!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider